workflows are standalone .yml file ad need to live in the workflows folders of the other repos 
```
jobs:
  publish-pages:
    uses: WCRP-CMIP/CMIPLD/.github/workflows/pages.yml@main
    with:
      branch: production
      force: true
    secrets:
      token: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}
```


composite actions are in the folders located here 

